name: NSKeyedArchiverDelegate
desc: The optional methods implemented by the delegate of a keyed archiver.

items.name: func archiver(NSKeyedArchiver, didEncode: Any?)
items.desc: Informs the delegate that a given object has been encoded.

items.name: func archiverDidFinish(NSKeyedArchiver)
items.desc: Notifies the delegate that encoding has finished.

items.name: func archiver(NSKeyedArchiver, willEncode: Any) -> Any?
items.desc: Informs the delegate that object is about to be encoded.

items.name: func archiverWillFinish(NSKeyedArchiver)
items.desc: Notifies the delegate that encoding is about to finish.

items.name: func archiver(NSKeyedArchiver, willReplace: Any?, with: Any?)
items.desc: Informs the delegate that one given object is being substituted for another given object.
